<h1 id="whatistextareajsorg">What is textarea.js.org</h1>
<p>Textarea is a subdomain provided by GitHub to show static pages, and .js.org is the provider.</p>
<h1 id="whattextareajsorghas">What textarea.js.org has</h1>
<ul>
<li>Syntax Highlighting</li>
<li>Good font</li>
<li>No distractions</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="and">And?</h1>
<ul>
<li>External content loading "?load=&lt;url&gt;"</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="thstsit">That's it?</h1>
